<plot>Yuji staggers through the madness of Shinjuku, where desire has run out of hope. Homeless people, lost children, office workers, non-stop traffic, low-level punks, phantoms and suicidals - there's no time, no room to think about what you've lost. Sometimes all you can see is the edge.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?188289</url></doc>
